author: Ben Kesslen
title: New Orleans Jazz Fest fall reschedule date cancelled, next concert to be in 2021
description: "It takes something truly momentous to interrupt a 50-year New Orleans tradition," the organization said in a statement.
content:
The New Orleans Jazz Fest 2020 announced that its fall reschedule date has been cancelled and the next concert won't occur until 2021.
